originalText.text: Most frustrating experience attempting to place an order with Lancome using the Afterpay service for installment payments.  After several attempts the order would absolutely not go through even with the store agent assistance.  I eventually placed the order using the same credit card I used to set up the Afterpay service and the order immediately went through with no problem.  Why advertise a service for customers  that your business will absolutely not allow them to use.  False advertising!

originalText.text: Was having difficulties to place order on Lancôme website but somehow I managed to do it.Got confirmation email and was told I will be emailed when the item is shipped.Waited for over ten days -no email ,no package .Called Lancôme customer service -the girl just said it was Cancelled!! I was Never notified that there was a problem and was waiting for the package ! To my question why it happened ,what was the problem I was told that it was some issue but not clear what was wrong and I have to order again !! I said that I will use the same exact information and the girl said just to order again ! Such a disappointing experience.Will just go to Macy’s next time I need something!
